Hans Leidekker (7):
      winhttp: Avoid a crash when the connection is closed while handling a redirect.
      wbemprox: Implement Win32_NetworkAdapter.GUID.
      wbemprox/tests: Add tests for Win32_NetworkAdapter/Configuration.
